cloud-architecture-diagram

// Define groups and nodes
User [icon: user]
Net [icon: internet-explorer]
IGW [icon: aws-internet-gateway]

VPC [icon: aws-vpc] {
  Public Server {
    Server SSH [icon: aws-ec2]
    Nat [icon: aws-nat-gateway]
  }

  RTF Table [icon: aws-auto-scaling]

  Private Server [color: red] {
    Win [icon: aws-ec2]
    Lin [icon: aws-ec2]
  }
}

// Define connections
IGW > Server SSH
Server SSH > RTF Table
RTF Table > Win, Lin
IGW < Nat < RTF Table
RTF Table < Win, Lin
Net > IGW
Net < IGW
User > IGW